      "description": "Hey there! I'm selling my absolute pride and joy. This beauty is in incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It's been garage-kept and pampered since day one. No scratches, no dents, and the interior is still smelling fresh and spotless. You really won't find one in better condition! I\u2019m sad to see it go, but I know the next owner is going to absolutely love it. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
