    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a concours-level E46 M3, featuring the legendary S54 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six. This specimen maintains impeccable mechanical integrity, with the dual-VANOS system recently overhauled and the rear subframe professionally reinforced for structural rigidity. Power is delivered through a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual transmission to a variable M-differential lock. The chassis dynamics are sharpened by factory-spec suspension with zero bushing play. Finished in Carbon Black over Nappa leather, the exterior retains its factory luster with no paint correction required. A true turnkey example for the discerning collector seeking peak atmospheric induction and analog feedback.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
