      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a true showroom-quality masterpiece that defies its age. This vehicle is in pristine, 'time capsule' condition, featuring a flawless exterior with a deep, mirror-like luster and absolutely no chips or swirl marks. Inside, the cabin retains its original factory scent; the premium leather remains supple and creaseless, while every button and digital display functions with crisp precision. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach, having been stored in a climate-controlled environment and serviced exclusively by specialists. The engine bay is immaculate, and the drive is as tight and responsive as the day it was first delivered. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning collector to own an investment-grade vehicle that requires nothing but a new home.",
