      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 2008 BMW M3 (E92) in Interlagos Blue. This specimen features the legendary S65 4.0L V8, utilizing individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS to achieve an 8,400 RPM redline. The powertrain is mated to a precise 6-speed manual transmission and a Variable M Differential Lock. This vehicle is mechanically superlative: the rod bearings have been proactively replaced with VAC Motorsports coated bearings, and the throttle actuators are upgraded. The chassis remains factory-spec with an unblemished carbon fiber roof and Electronic Damper Control (EDC). Zero subframe issues or fluid seepage. The interior is preserved in pristine Novillo leather, reflecting a level of care suitable for any serious collection.",
